Most guilds won't even attempt them, some will but how can you seriously justify telling others that they cant even try???  Why play a game?  For the challenge or to get the best equipment possible regardless of the cost or to be with friends?  I play for the challenge of mobs and my friends, all I was asking is why can't they be moved to fcfs?  I was told my answer, the leaders of Tindi, BoTs and NB have decided that THEY, not the people of the rathe make that choice and THEY said no.  End of discussion thank you for your answer and sorry for all of my rambling.   See you all in game. <p><center><BR><font color= Blue><BR><i>Granitfist/Jeribu<i/><BR><i>GrandMaster/High Priest<i/><BR><i>Co-Leader of Circles End<i/><BR><i>The Rathe<BR><center><i><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370733">The Monk </> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370756">The Cleric<i/>
